-	notification_parameters*, property_group*, instance*,
-	stability?, template? ) >
-
-<!ATTLIST service
-	name		CDATA #REQUIRED
-	version		CDATA #REQUIRED
-	type		( service | restarter | milestone ) #REQUIRED >
